FeedPackage.Description: Excqape interfaces provide support for the combination of several design patterns: the Command Pattern, the Decorator Pattern, and the 'Exchange' Pattern. It abstracts any storage paradigm (relational, key-value, document, etc.), without the ugliness of repositories.

FeedPackage.Summary: Excqape is simply DAL and CQRS support interfaces.
